data_first <- data_1 %>% filter(label==1)
data_second <- data_1 %>% filter(label==2)
data_three <- data_1 %>% filter(label==3)
name <- c("1","2","3")
mean_1 <- c(mean(data_first$q_remind_Parents), 
            mean(data_second$q_remind_Parents),
            mean(data_three$q_remind_Parents))
mean_2 <- c(mean(data_first$q_remind_Siblings), 
            mean(data_second$q_remind_Siblings),
            mean(data_three$q_remind_Siblings))
mean_3 <- c(mean(data_first$q_remind_Friends), 
            mean(data_second$q_remind_Friends),
            mean(data_three$q_remind_Friends))
mean_4 <- c(mean(data_first$q_remind_Teacher), 
            mean(data_second$q_remind_Teacher),
            mean(data_three$q_remind_Teacher))

data.frame(name, mean_1) %>%
  ggplot(aes(x=name, y=mean_1)) +
  geom_bar(stat="identity", fill="steelblue")+
  geom_text(aes(label=round(mean_1, 2)), vjust=-0.3, size=3.5)+
  theme_minimal() +
  scale_y_continuous(limits=c(0,1)) +
  labs(y= "q_remind_Parents", x = "label")

data.frame(name, mean_2) %>%
  ggplot(aes(x=name, y=mean_2)) +
  geom_bar(stat="identity", fill="steelblue")+
  geom_text(aes(label=round(mean_2, 2)), vjust=-0.3, size=3.5)+
  theme_minimal() +
  scale_y_continuous(limits=c(0,1)) +
  labs(y= "q_remind_Siblings", x = "label")

data.frame(name, mean_3) %>%
  ggplot(aes(x=name, y=mean_3), ylim=c(0,1)) +
  geom_bar(stat="identity", fill="steelblue")+
  geom_text(aes(label=round(mean_3, 2)), vjust=-0.3, size=3.5)+
  theme_minimal() +
  scale_y_continuous(limits=c(0,1)) +
  labs(y= "q_remind_Friends", x = "label")
